description: This Chainlink VRF hall of fame Parvati purrs with a rating of 66, and a multiplier of 5x. It has a total score of 330, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 3 for North, Leverage for East, Stringalong for South, and 1 for West. Parvati has the personality suit of punter. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Parvati [330 Votes, Hall of Fame]
